<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">
  Fuwaly
</h1>

<p class="text-gray-700 text-center mb-10">
  今の気持ちにそっと寄り添う、やさしいタロット占い
</p>

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10">
  <div class="p-4 border rounded-lg bg-white shadow">
    <p class="font-semibold">🌞 本日の運勢</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">
      今日の流れを占う
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="p-4 border rounded-lg bg-white shadow">
    <p class="font-semibold">💖 ジャンル別占い</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">
      恋愛・仕事・人間関係
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="p-4 border rounded-lg bg-white shadow">
    <p class="font-semibold">🌿 感情から占う</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">
      今の気持ちを言葉に
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
  <% if user_signed_in? %>
    <%= link_to "マイページへ",
        user_path(current_user),
        class: "px-6 py-2 rounded bg-purple-600 text-white hover:bg-purple-700" %>

    <%= button_to "ログアウト",
        destroy_user_session_path,
        method: :delete,
        class: "px-6 py-2 rounded border border-gray-400 text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100" %>
  <% else %>
    <%= link_to "ログイン",
        new_user_session_path,
        class: "px-6 py-2 rounded bg-purple-600 text-white hover:bg-purple-700" %>

    <%= link_to "新規登録",
        new_user_registration_path,
        class: "px-6 py-2 rounded border border-purple-600 text-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-50" %>
  <% end %>
</div>
